column5: looks like you got out fished again ....i think you should sign over ownership of this forum to the real fisher in the family
hey I did alright.. lol  I caught this monster.. lol
I saw the same size fish twice. Difference being, the first photo was much better. It clearly showed the color and condition of the fish to it's full extent, not just a bunch of background.
TJ, you've just revealed a secret and internet super heros have kept a secret for ages!!!!!!
If the camera added two pounds to this one ....i think you owe the camera company about a pound and a half of free advertising...
They look like one pound bass in both pics.........
Where did you buy the lure to catch it?
Actually... i have them in stock and was trying them out before putting them on sale.. its a curved minnow with a really unique action when slowly retrieved.
When are you going to catch a walleye up there?
